From fe27543b55e55b71cbba1502d7f569058111e0f9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Andris PE <neandris@gmail.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:54:55 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 8/9] Parse states before (quick) loopback accept

Suggested at
https://forum.openwrt.org/t/first-rule-in-chain-input-output-for-firewall4/204723
Formally speeds up "default" nat function over loopback ipc.
